        <span class="member">Lord Filkin</span> moved Amendment No. 239A:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0651P0-03567'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0651P0_20030710_GCR_301' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
