          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-joyce-anelay" title="Ms Joyce Anelay">Baroness Anelay of St Johns</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            As ever, the Minister has a very courteous way of saying, "No". I beg leave to withdraw the amendment.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
